* = 24bit/44.1khz
+ = 16bit/44.1khz
× = 24bit/48khz
÷ = 24bit/96khz

all tracks are flac except for the Dead Flowers EP and Four the Record deluxe edition studio album. Dead Flowers EP is wav. Four the Record deluxe edition studio album is alac
